callOfDuty

Class Target

  • java.lang.Object
    • callOfDuty.Target
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Armory, Barrack, Ground, HeadQuarter, OilDrum, SentryTower, Tank

    public abstract class Target
extends java.lang.Object
    The Target class represents the attacked target in the game callofDuty. The Target class provides the basic methods the user need in the game. Author Jingxuan Bao and Yaoqi Deng in 25/11/2021
